styles.content: @keyframes keys{0%{border-color:#684414 #684414 transparent transparent}25%{border-color:#0077be #0077be transparent transparent}50%{border-color:#c0edff #c0edff transparent transparent}75%{border-color:#e25822 #e25822 transparent transparent}100%{border-color:#684414 #684414 transparent transparent}}*{margin:0;padding:0}html,body{width:100%;height:100%;font-size:1.5vmax}.wrapper{width:100%;height:100%;position:relative;background:#eee;background-image:repeating-linear-gradient(45deg,transparent 0,transparent 28px,rgba(0,0,0,.02) 28px,rgba(0,0,0,.02) 30px,transparent 30px),repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg,transparent 0,transparent 28px,rgba(0,0,0,.02) 28px,rgba(0,0,0,.02) 30px,transparent 30px)}.header{width:100%;height:40%;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;text-transform:uppercase;font:1.9em Verdana,sans-serif;padding-top:16.5%}.header .subtext{font-size:.4em;line-height:2.2em;display:block}.content{width:100%;height:60%}.menu{width:100%;padding:50px 10px 10px 10px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;list-style:none;text-transform:uppercase}.menu .item{padding:10px 24px;display:inline-block;background:#fff;border-bottom:2px solid #ccc;cursor:pointer;margin-right:5px;transition:all .1s ease-in-out;color:#111}.menu .item:hover{transform:scale(1.05)}.menu .item.fire:hover{border-color:#e25822}.menu .item.earth:hover{border-color:#684414}.menu .item.air:hover{border-color:#c0edff}.menu .item.water:hover{border-color:#0077be}.corner-indicator{animation:keys 5s ease-in-out;animation-iteration-count:infinite;position:absolute;width:0;height:0;top:0;right:0;border-width:25px;border-style:solid;border-color:rgba(55,155,255,1) rgba(55,155,255,1) transparent transparent;display:block}

scripts.content: import Router from'../router.js';import Route from'../route.js';import View from'../View.js';import LazyView from'../lazyview.js';import ViewsBundledRoute from'../ViewsBundledRoute.js';import LazyViewsBundledRoute from'../LazyViewsBundledRoute.js';window.onload=()=>{const router=new Router({basename:'http://0.0.0.0:3000/example',useRouterTag:true,routes:[new LazyViewsBundledRoute('/earth','http://0.0.0.0:3000/example/earth/code.json',{}),new LazyViewsBundledRoute('/water','http://0.0.0.0:3000/example/water/code.json',{}),new LazyViewsBundledRoute('/air','http://0.0.0.0:3000/example/air/code.json',{}),new LazyViewsBundledRoute('/fire','http://0.0.0.0:3000/example/fire/code.json',{}),],});const earthButton=document.querySelector('.menu .item.earth');const waterButton=document.querySelector('.menu .item.water');const airButton=document.querySelector('.menu .item.air');const fireButton=document.querySelector('.menu .item.fire');earthButton.addEventListener('click',()=>router.push('/earth'),false);waterButton.addEventListener('click',()=>router.push('/water'),false);airButton.addEventListener('click',()=>router.push('/air'),false);fireButton.addEventListener('click',()=>router.push('/fire'),false);}
